\v 19 \x - \xo 11:19 \xt Ibr 9.4; PA 8.5; 15.5; 16.21\x*K…®la am…®n da yaŇč mudaŇčakwa, aŇčelo da PiŇčkop dakon Telag…® Yut Madep Kwen Kokup tosok uŇčun w…®tdalgwit. AŇčakwa PiŇčkop dakon SaŇčbek SaŇčbek K…®nam Telag…® Yut Madepmon taŇčban kawit. Mal da dukwan dukwan yamaŇčakwan k…®r…®r…®Ňč uŇčun wuw…®k madepsi yag…®t. AŇčakwan m…®kt…®m wud…®p aŇčakwan ais morapm…® s…®kak da yaŇč mawit.   
\ms1 Sunduk gat am…®n kab…®ni gat wag…®lsi tas…®k tawit  
