\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt Dan 7.7\x*Ae kundukon t…®lak k…®nda gat noman tag…®t. T…®lak uŇčun yaŇč: nug…®m yokwisi g…®pt…®m…® gami madepsi k…®nda noman tag…®t. UŇčun nug…®m yokwisi uŇčun busuŇčni 7 kab…®. AŇčakwan jom…® 10 yaŇč busuŇč…®kon kwawit. AŇčakwan k…®la am…®n madep pel…®t 7 kab…® da busuŇč…®kon tawit. \fig Nug…®m busuŇč…® 7 kab…®|alt="Dragon" src="Dragon.tif" size="span" loc="Location" copy="Copyright" ref="12.3" \fig*   
