\v 7 \x - \xo 12:7 \xt Jut 9\x*K…®l…® Kwen Kokup emat madepsi k…®nda noman tag…®t. Maikel gat aŇčelo kab…®ni gat nug…®m yokwisi madep uŇčun gat emat wamgwit. Ae nug…®m yokwisi madep gat ae aŇčelo kab…®ni k…®si emat kobog…® awit.  
\v 8 Mani emaron teban toni dakon tapm…®m d…®ma taŇč yomgut, do Kwen Kokup ae saŇčbeŇček d…®ma eg…®pgwit.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt WW 3.1,14; Lk 10.18; 22.31; PA 20.2\x*PiŇčkop dakon aŇčelo da nug…®m yokwisi madep maba p…®g…®g…®t. Nug…®m yokwisi madep uŇčun kal…®psigwan eg…®pgut, m…®kt…®mon am…®n morap yokwi ani do paŇčkewaldak. Mani k…®nda KoŇč, ae mani k…®nda Sunduk yaŇč yoŇč. UŇčun maba m…®kt…®mon p…®g…®t, ae aŇčeloni k…®si uŇčun gat maba p…®wit.   
