\c 13  
\s1 JoŇč k…®lap yokwisi bamor…® noman tag…®mal  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt PA 12.3; 17.3,7-12\x*Ae kaŇčapbo joŇč k…®lap yokwisi k…®nda tap kagagwan da noman taŇč w…®g…®t. UŇčun busuŇč…® 7 kab…®. AŇčakwan jom…® 10 kab…® da busuŇč…®kon kwawit. AŇčakwa k…®la am…®n madep dakon pel…®t 10 kab…® jom…®kon tawit. Ae busuŇč…®kon man taŇč taŇč awit. Man uŇčun PiŇčkop j…®g…®lak mib…®l…® mib…®l…® yaŇč …®m…®m dakon man da tawit.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt Dan 7.4-6\x*JoŇč k…®lap yokwisi uŇčun kag…®m uŇčun joŇč pusiket madep lepat yaŇč yoŇč, uŇčun yombem. Mani kandapm…® uŇčun bea dakon yombem, ae gen kagani laion dakon yombem. Nug…®m yokwisi madep uŇčun da iy…® dakon tapm…®m, ae k…®la am…®n y…®ty…®t tamoni, ae k…®la agak dakon yaŇč dagok madepni, uŇčun joŇč k…®lap yokwisi do …®mgut.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt PA 17.8\x*UŇčun joŇč k…®lap yokwisi dakon busuŇč…® k…®nda si k…®mor…® da t…®lak wudani taŇč …®mgut, mani aeni k…®b…®dag…®t. AŇčakwan m…®kt…®mon m…®Ňčat am…®n morap k…®si uŇčun kaŇč n…®mn…®m…®gek yolgwit.  
\v 4 Nug…®m yokwisi madep uŇčun da joŇč k…®lap yokwisi do k…®la am…®n pi asak do yaŇč mudaŇč …®m…®k, do nug…®m yokwisi madep uŇčun gawak …®mgwit. Ae joŇč k…®lap yokwiyo k…®si gawak …®m…®Ňček yaŇč yawit, ‚ÄúNam…®n am…®n joŇč k…®lap yokwisi yombem? Ae nam…®n am…®n gat emat ar…®pm…® tag…® wamjil?‚ÄĚ   
